MBOMBELA &#8211; Lowvelder recently published two articles about the Cradle of Life animal sanctuary which the owner of this facility considered inaccurate and unfair.The conservation development is home to a number of predators which includes various big cat species.Since publication more information has come to the newspaper s attention and a follow up article will be published in next week s edition of the newspaper.Fred Daniels, who has been involved with the development of Cradle of Mankind since its inception almost twenty years ago, will be interviewed by Lowvelder this weekend to shed light on some of the controversies and questions that have been raised.